You step out into this forest, hit a hot wave of humid air.

6
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:16,000
Not too far. A clearing.

7
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,400
I think we can follow the path there.

8
00:00:19,400 --> 00:00:21,400
Okay. Yeah, that's our best bet.

9
