And then was like, nah, even though my character's still around, I got to go my separate ways.

55
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,400
It's fair.

56
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,000
That's understandable.

57
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,800
I mean, a goth is around, obviously, because we're...

58
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:55,200
Yeah, a goth and rax are out having adventures, doing cool stuff.

59
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,400
They got their own things to do.

60
